Third-party notices

The hosted converter web app (web/) ships a WebAssembly build of FFmpeg
(ffmpeg.wasm, https://github.com/ffmpegwasm/ffmpeg.wasm) compiled with
libx264. FFmpeg is licensed under the LGPL/GPL; the included build enables
GPL components (x264), so the deployed converter binary is distributed under
the terms of the GNU General Public License v2 or later
(https://www.ffmpeg.org/legal.html, https://www.videolan.org/developers/x264.html).
The source code for FFmpeg and x264 is available at the URLs above. The
repository's own source code remains MIT-licensed.
